課程教材 Course Material
	    “Introduction to Combustion” by W.C. Strahle, Belgale House, 2nd ed., 1996.“Combustion” by J. Warnatz, U. Maas, R.W. Dibble, Springer-Verlag, 2nd ed., 1999.    

參考書目 References
	    “An introduction to combustion: concepts and applications” by S. R. Turns, McGraw-Hill, 1996.“Combustion Physics” by Chung K. Law, Cambridge University Press, 2006.    

