課程概述 Course Description
       讓修習本課程學生瞭解燃燒現象及燃燒科技相關理論與工程實務基礎。修習本課程後學生應熟悉燃燒基本原理，包括燃燒相關基本熱力學、化學與物理理論、預混火焰、非預混(擴散)火焰、燃燒點火過程、火焰穩駐現象與機構、紊流燃燒、液滴與噴霧燃燒、高速燃燒等。To facilitate the students with the required background and theoretical fundamentals to understand the combustion phenomena and combustion science and engineering, including: combustion thermodynamics, physics, and chemistry, phenomena and theory of premixed, nonpremixed flames, ignition, flame stabilization, turbulent flames, droplet and spray combustion, and high-speed combustion etc.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives


